subject: Basketball (College)
lead_paragraph: Sam Dekker scored 17 points, and Nigel Hayes’s tip-in with 20 seconds left capped his 15-point day as Wisconsin rallied to beat Georgetown in the Battle 4 Atlantis semifinals in Paradise Island, Bahamas.
